{"tid":49963,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紅魔連奴：大陸金？不了","createTime":"2016-12-22T05:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T07:33:08.000Z","uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"836a68e9ce22020d8651df99e20ad247b2877037","tid":49963,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:47:23.000Z","msg":"近年嚟唔少大牌球員都喜歡去新世界掘金，除咗土超、美職之外，最畀得起錢嘅一定係偉大祖國啦。日前轉出「泰維斯61.5萬鎊周薪投申花」嘅恐怖數字，呢個價可以請得起2個30萬先生朗尼！咁摩連奴又想唔想去掘下金呢？你認為呢？<br />\n<br />\n佢咁答：「大陸金係人人都想掘嘅，不過我都係喜歡最高水準嘅足球多啲。我先53歲，要去中國太後生喇。咁我咪要喺中國呢啲地方耗費好長嘅人生？我想留喺最高難度、最難贏嘅地方，所以我依家身在正確的地方。所以呢，<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然曼聯未同我講過續約，我亦唔期望仲有3年約的情況下佢嚟提出呢件事，不過曼聯真係好支持我，畀到我3年一定唔係最終年期嘅感覺我。佢哋知我各方面都好愛呢到，我喜歡曼聯的工作，而且佢哋知道只要遞上合約，我咪埋眼都會簽咗佢。就算我經理人唔在場我都會照簽，因為我真係好愛呢份工。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n好喇，講完佢有幾想續約，不如都係講下我哋隊波啦！摩帥講到一月佢盡可能都唔想買人，因為冬季窗始終有限制：「一如以往，我重申我好滿意曼聯人腳。而且我相信夏季轉會窗多啲，因為時間又多啲，選擇又多啲，咩都好啲。所以都係睇定啲先啦！至於離隊，我哋畀球員走唔係因為我哋逼佢，只會係佢想走我哋先會畀佢走。要我講的話，我寧願留低隊中球員多過想佢哋走。呢一刻其實我都仲有啲bad feelings，因為我無辦法畀到每個球員足夠的時間去證明自己，因為好多位置都人滿之患。好似楊格、迪比，我無機會畀一連串的比賽佢哋去作戰、去證明自己。感覺真係唔多好。盧祖同埋鐘斯我就非常滿意喇，盧祖一直都被人話佢唔夠班打曼聯，而鐘斯亦因為唔穩定同成日傷，以前都畀人睇低一線。所以我對於佢哋嘅好表現感到好欣慰。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://football.fanpiece.com/m/manutd/c1259221.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fmanutd%2Fc1259221.html&d=TNOiLsxCBh2L6hAYJQdfLmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=bea9d799\" target=\"_blank\">http://football.fanpiece.com/m/manutd/c1259221.html</a><br />\n<br />\nDaddy真曼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4361160d9a53127d465661d6544801c0a22bb85","tid":49963,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:48:08.000Z","msg":"躝啦摩狗"},{"pid":"cf091b7e7beed2f4152c7049822bbfcce007f908","tid":49963,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>躝啦摩狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f1acd7488803ff1eaaf8494a20b823a9fbd108","tid":49963,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BbvKC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBbvKC.gif&h=bd6358e8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BbvKC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBbvKC.gif&h=bd6358e8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BbvKC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBbvKC.gif&h=bd6358e8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BbvKC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBbvKC.gif&h=bd6358e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6bd6f59b53e1e8c09a87778174788a50492f9da","tid":49963,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6ae888454fdda93169905aa813bde649bcd6c9","tid":49963,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf2b550a6e917395a06c452c9b55c1c07346c14","tid":49963,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}